---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Pricing">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-center text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Free and open source. Forever.</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-center text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">FeatureSignals is Apache-2.0 licensed. Self-host on your own infrastructure with zero licensing fees.</p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-indigo-600 p-8 text-left relative shadow-lg shadow-indigo-100">
        <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-white">Self-Hosted</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Community Edition</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">$0<span class="text-base font-normal text-slate-500"> forever</span></p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Unlimited projects &amp; environments</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Unlimited flags &amp; evaluations</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Unlimited team members</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>A/B experimentation</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>RBAC &amp; audit logs</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Approval workflows</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Webhooks, scheduling, kill switch</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Relay proxy</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>All 5 SDKs + OpenFeature</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Community support (GitHub)</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/docs/getting-started/quickstart" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white transition-all hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:shadow-md">Get Started</a>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-8 text-left transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:border-slate-300">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Enterprise Support</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Custom</p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Everything in Community</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Priority support (4h SLA)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Deployment assistance</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Custom integrations</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>Training &amp; onboarding</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="mailto:support@featuresignals.com" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg border border-slate-300 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-400">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Estimated self-hosting costs</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500">All you pay for is your infrastructure.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-left">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Small Team</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">~$10<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500">/month</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">Single VPS (2 CPU, 4GB RAM) on Hetzner or DigitalOcean. Runs all services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Growing Team</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">~$30<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500">/month</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">API server + separate PostgreSQL. Add relay proxy for edge deployment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Scale</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">~$50+<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500">/month</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">Multi-instance API behind load balancer. Relay proxies per region. Managed PostgreSQL.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
